{"tid":2254043,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有過情緒困擾","createTime":"2020-10-22T14:10:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T12:36:20.000Z","uid":112191,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"18b9229b441566cb79bb42128b646e67c0f90c14","tid":2254043,"uid":112191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1iF4nrx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1iF4nrx.jpg&h=c322be97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是咁的，我同幾個朋友想整一個app去幫大家改善情緒健康。有呢個idea好單純就係因為我地想幫人同自己。<br />\n<br />\n我地幾個都有過大大小小嘅情緒困擾...我一直都有情緒管理問題，之前用過mood tracking/ meditation (headspace)之類嘅apps，但都冇動力keep住用。我好希望有個app係大家都會想持續咁用落去，真係幫到人。<br />\n<br />\n另一個partner就因為工作好唔開心，曾經試過係夜晚打比輔導熱線，但發現十個有十個都唔聽。佢心諗：如果有人想自殺，佢一早死左啦？<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個比較重要既原因，係我地幾個都一致想做既，就係為手足提供一個安全既平台去抒發自己，因為我知道呢到都有好多人同我地一樣，可能因為種種原因而未能夠同人傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n而家你可以幫到我地嘅，就係填左份問卷，等我地知道香港人需要一個點嘅app。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/XnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FXnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRBAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=3c8f2758\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/XnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7</a><br />\n<strong>！！！所有資料絕對保密！！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n整個咁既app出黎唔容易，但如果大家幫手俾意見，就有可能成事。歡迎係問卷留名同 telegram 交流下。<br />\n<br />\n花5-10分鐘填左佢！好人一生平安！"},{"pid":"367f9d63b5409106fd08df67e3f0df1692c6ae6c","tid":2254043,"uid":112191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T11:33:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"edd534b31b4e989abadc5bd03dfc0a7244c1ba84","tid":2254043,"uid":380260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T21:45:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"47f237e3599703670bd65997257a7c58de7ae11f","tid":2254043,"uid":112191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;push"},{"pid":"554c69d822028088e48add32257ff97fd2c1a210","tid":2254043,"uid":112191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy